Love and lust, passion and desire, man and woman, Hong Kong Hong Kong. A critically acclaimed drama from the Hong Kong New Wave, Hong Kong Hong Kong sizzles with erotic tension in relating the destruction of three lives involved in a triangular relationship: a macho Thai-Chinese rogue [Alex Man Chi-leung], a prosperous, middle-aged carpenter [Kwan Hoi-shan], and the sultry, beautiful illegal immigrant they both love [Cherie Chung Cho-hung, in one of her most acclaimed roles].
